      <title>台湾前总统候选人因腐败被捕</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-31/former-taiwan-opposition-leader-held-on-corruption-allegations</link>
      <description><![CDATA[台湾反对党前主席柯文哲因担任台北市长期间发生的房地产开发丑闻，在经过近19个小时的审讯后被逮捕。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-31/former-taiwan-opposition-leader-held-on-corruption-allegations</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 31 Aug 2024 04:07:39 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
